    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对所有美国商品的税额缴纳了34％的特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-imposes-34-tariffs-on-all-us-imports-as-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国通过一系列措施对新的美国关税进行报复，包括对所有美国进口和稀土的出口控制的征税，并与唐纳德·特朗普总统进行了贸易斗争升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/china-imposes-34-tariffs-on-all-us-imports-as-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EM资产随着中国的报复而受到打击，欧洲计算关税费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，特朗普政府对新兴市场的全面关税产生的影响，由于对经济冲击的期望提高，欧洲资产下降了，中国宣布了泰特（Tit-Tat）的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着工作数据增加市场焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/treasuries-hold-4-line-as-jobs-report-powell-speech-loom-large</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税又使市场的影响又使市场降低了今年，交易者进一步提高了对美联储今年削减利益率的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/treasuries-hold-4-line-as-jobs-report-powell-speech-loom-large</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
